<h2>EasyRec 1.11</h2>
<ul>
<li>Menu bar recording control — red dot icon with timer during recording (like QuickTime)</li>
<li>Switch between floating bar, main window, or hidden mode while recording</li>
<li>Stop recording from the menu bar dropdown</li>
<li>Dock click restores main window during recording</li>
</ul>
